Title: Fine Dining
Description:
In my living years, I was the greatest warrior of the swarm.

Help me regain my strength, and I shall show you.

I smell the salt sea nearby, and where you can find the sea, you will find briny clackers.

Bring me their tails. I must feast upon their flesh.
CompletionText: I have much work to do. The sooner I can fight, the sooner I can return to the Council.
RewardText: Excellent. This shall give me the strength to vanquish my foes.
